        "rich_text_rJaBdp": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Introduction",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>A trilogy ring, also known as a three-stone ring, is one of the most meaningful styles in diamond jewellery. Instead of featuring a single center diamond, this design includes three stones placed side by side. While the look itself is elegant, the real charm of a trilogy ring lies in its symbolism. </p><p>Each stone in the ring tells a story. For many people, the three diamonds represent the past, present, and future of a relationship. This meaning is why trilogy rings are often chosen for engagements, anniversaries, and milestone celebrations.</p><p>At Lucira Jewelry, trilogy rings combine thoughtful symbolism with contemporary design. Pieces like the Three-Stone 0.91ct Round Diamond Ring, Pear Diamond Three-Stone Ring, and Hexa Baguette Trilogy Ring show how this classic concept can be interpreted in many different ways. </p><p>Let’s explore what makes trilogy rings so meaningful.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_qw7HLy": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "The Past, Present, and Future Meaning Behind Trilogy Rings",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>The Past, Present, and Future Meaning Behind Trilogy Rings</h2>",
            "custom_id": "the-past",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_A8fUE6": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Rich Text ",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>The most common interpretation of a trilogy ring is the idea of past, present, and future.</p><p>1.] The first stone represents the journey you’ve already shared.<br/><br/>2.] The center stone symbolizes the love and commitment you feel today.<br/><br/>3.] The third stone represents the future you are building together.<br/><br/>This meaning makes trilogy rings particularly special for engagements or anniversary gifts. The design becomes more than jewellery - it reflects a relationship’s story.</p><p>Rings like the<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/products/three-stone-oval-anniversary-ring\" target=\"_blank\" title=\" Three-Stone Oval Anniversary Ring\"> Three-Stone Oval Anniversary Ring</a> from Lucira capture this sentiment beautifully, making them a meaningful choice for couples celebrating important milestones.</p>",
            "custom_id": "color",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_C4KUKT": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "name": "Image With Text",
          "settings": {
