        "rich_text_DGeVUi": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Trilogy Rings Are Often Chosen for Engagements and Anniversaries",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Trilogy Rings Are Often Chosen for Engagements and Anniversaries</h2>",
            "custom_id": "trilogy",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_gqV6WF": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>While trilogy rings can be worn as fashion jewellery, they are especially popular for engagement and anniversary rings.</p><p>For engagements, the three diamonds symbolize the journey of a couple's relationship - where they started, where they are today, and where they’re going together.</p><p>For anniversaries, the design can represent the years already shared and the many more to come.</p><p>Lucira’s Oval and<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/round-rings\" target=\"_blank\" title=\" Round Diamond \"> Round Diamond </a>Trilogy Ring and Emerald, Oval, and Round Diamond Trilogy Ring are great examples of rings that feel meaningful yet modern.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_jHyzad": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Trilogy Rings Offer More Sparkle Than a Solitaire",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Trilogy Rings Offer More Sparkle Than a Solitaire</h2>",
            "custom_id": "trilogy-rings",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_ngTfTe": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Another reason people love trilogy rings is the extra brilliance they provide.</p><p>Because there are three diamonds instead of one, the ring naturally reflects more light. The side stones add sparkle while still allowing the center stone to remain the main focus.</p><p>Designs like the Multi-Shape Diamond Trilogy Ring show how multiple stones can create a bright, lively look without feeling overly elaborate.</p><p>For buyers who want more sparkle than a solitaire ring but still prefer a classic style, trilogy rings are often the perfect choice. </p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
