          "name": "Modern Trilogy Rings Blend Tradition With Contemporary Design ",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Modern Trilogy Rings Blend Tradition With Contemporary Design </h2><p>Although trilogy rings have been around for many years, modern jewellery designers continue to reinterpret the style.</p><p>Today’s trilogy rings may include:</p>",
            "custom_id": "modern-trilogy",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_Rhphdr": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>1.] Mixed diamond shapes<br/>2.] Sleek modern bands<br/>3.] Unique stone arrangements<br/><br/>The Hexa Trillion Trilogy Ring and Modern Trio Pear Diamond Ring from Lucira demonstrate how traditional symbolism can be combined with contemporary design ideas.</p><p>This blend of meaning and creativity keeps trilogy rings relevant even as jewellery trends evolve.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_tt6yxH": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Lucira’s Approach to Trilogy Ring Design",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Lucira’s Approach to Trilogy Ring Design</h2><p>At<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\" Lucira Jewelry\"> Lucira Jewelry</a>, trilogy rings are crafted with the idea that jewellery should tell a story.</p><p>Each design highlights the beauty of the three stones while maintaining balance and elegance. Lucira rings feature IGI-certified lab-grown diamonds, offering exceptional brilliance with responsible sourcing.</p><p>Whether you prefer classic round diamonds or a combination of unique shapes, Lucira’s trilogy rings are designed to celebrate meaningful moments in life.</p>",
            "custom_id": "lucira",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        }
